flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Detection of a critical issue or non-conformance in production.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Detect critical issue or non-conformance]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Monitoring - Analyze issue severity and context]
  N2 --> N3{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Determine appropriate action}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Execute selected action]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Cortex Monitoring - Monitor and validate action effectiveness]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Notification - Notify stakeholders]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Faster containment, optimized rework, minimized scrap, and accelerated root-cause remediation leading to reduced COGS and improved OTIF and line efficiency.]
  N3 -->|Issue severity exceeds predefined thr...| B1[Escalate to higher management]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Higher management reviews and approves further actions.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Insufficient data for decision| B2[Request additional information]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Additional data is collected and re-evaluated.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Action fails or does not resolve issue| B3[Initiate root cause analysis]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Conduct RCA to identify underlying causes and implement corrective actions.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]